    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Connected→Idle→Sending→Idle的循环画好了，Idle→Closed也加上了。需要处理超时逻辑吗？比如Sending卡住的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
